				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ai-S%C3%ADnh/poem-8zIo1kpqK4yBRE9YrLewIw">Ai Sính - 哀郢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3o-tam-ni%C3%AAn-Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-khoa-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-danh-k%C3%BD/poem-lmPI_Y7GazogxyWzI82qMg">Đại Bảo tam niên Nhâm Tuất khoa tiến sĩ đề danh ký - 大寶弎年壬戌科進士題名記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/%C4%90%E1%BA%BF-kinh-thi%C3%AAn/poem-9NRXjE-zAkH_P0dE0rQmRA">Đế kinh thiên - 帝京篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-jvbfrjspi2Y6S8b3jeqzpA">Lạc Tân Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-H%C3%A3ng/Gi%E1%BA%A3n-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-Du-T%E1%BA%ADp-Nh%E1%BA%A5t-L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%BF-C%E1%BA%A9n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-v4ZXJ8pEkmLEgIN1TZVfvQ">Giản Triều Tiên quốc sứ Du Tập Nhất, Lý Thế Cẩn kỳ 2 - 簡朝鮮國使俞集一，李世瑾其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C3%B4ng-H%C3%A3ng/author-fN6vfxH4UNedI1oRF5kt2Q">Nguyễn Công Hãng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-C%C6%A1/Ph%C3%B3-L%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-Zk2NBjgvPF8X6LuaYtDNWg">Phó Lạc Đạo trung tác - 赴洛道中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-C%C6%A1/author-EfNc8fssq4nwf0WjqNOWdA">Lục Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Qu%C3%A1-quan-l%C6%B0u-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Phan-ng%E1%BB%B1-s%E1%BB%AD-V%C5%A9-c%C3%B4ng-b%E1%BB%99-Ng%C3%B4-hi%E1%BB%87p-tr%E1%BA%A5n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-AiefRx5No5gcRf7oULFf2w">Quá quan lưu tặng Phan ngự sử, Vũ công bộ, Ngô hiệp trấn kỳ 1 - 過關留贈潘御史武工部吳協鎮其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-nh%C6%B0-T%C3%A2y/poem-pBQ00B4mDV9dkz3Hdd8XBg">Tống Tây Hồ tiên sinh như Tây - 送西湖先生如西</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/author-tWIJ_JcBg9FILAgkriOf3g">Huỳnh Thúc Kháng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%B1u/Tranh-nghinh-k%E1%BB%B3-l%C3%A3o/poem-NwIgEiGckyB8jsxKN30n4A">Tranh nghinh kỳ lão - 爭迎耆老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%B1u/author-PX1pV4cjfZZCiPiOoAmgRg">Nguyễn Sư Hựu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Tu%C3%A2n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-l%E1%BB%99-1/poem-qmR1bI3xVqVdZFJPWKxt2w">Tuân đại lộ 1 - 遵大路 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Minh-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%91c-phong/poem-g-_bAvw1Zf8GtSrkqQxzKw">Vương Cốc phong - 王谷峰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Minh-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-0lEjWleAq81Vjk--u6V0CA">Trương Minh Lượng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
